---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Open Banking - The Davinci Project" description="Enable secure data sharing and financial innovation.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Open Banking</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Enable secure data sharing and financial innovation through open APIs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What is Open Banking?</h2>
      <p>Open Banking is a financial services model that enables third-party developers to build applications and services around financial institutions. Our protocol provides the secure infrastructure needed for open banking in the digital asset space.</p>
      
      <h2>Our Approach</h2>
      <p>The Davinci Project supports Open Banking through:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Standardized API endpoints for escrow services</li>
        <li>Secure data sharing with user consent</li>
        <li>Interoperability with traditional banking systems</li>
        <li>Transparent transaction history and reporting</li>
        <li>Compliance with global Open Banking standards</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Benefits</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Enhanced customer experience through integrated services</li>
        <li>Increased competition and innovation</li>
        <li>Better financial data management</li>
        <li>Seamless cross-platform transactions</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h3>Explore Open Banking possibilities</h3>
        <p>Learn how our open APIs can enable new financial products.</p>
        <a href="/api" class="btn btn-primary">View API Docs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .content-section p, .content-section li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .content-section ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  
  .btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-green);
    color: #000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 7rem 0 3rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
